// BaseLine
$colums:12
$gutter: (100% /$colums)* 0.05
$one: (100% / $colums)
$pc-1: 1000px
$large: 992px
$table: 600px
$mobile: 320px
$line: 16 * 1.618px
$base-line: 16px 
// BaseLine
html
  color: #000000
  font: 400 16px/#{$base-line} 'Oswald', sans-serif
body

  margin-bottom: $base-line * 2
  div
    box-sizing: border-box

    overflow: hidden

    @media (max-width: 318px)

        width: calc( (#{$one} * 6) - #{$gutter})
    @media ( min-width: $mobile) and (max-width: $table)

        &.s2

        &.s3

        &.s12

        &.lef-s1
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 1) + (#{$gutter} * 1))
        &.lef-s2
          margin-left: calc( (#{$one} * 2) + #{$gutter})
        &.lef-s3

        &.lef-s4

        &.lef-s5

//Animal-Rout
.anim
  animation: animationFrames linear 0.8s
  animation-iteration-count: 1
  transform-origin: 50% 50%
  -webkit-animation: animationFrames linear 0.8s
  -webkit-animation-iteration-count: 1
  -webkit-transform-origin: 50% 50%
  -moz-animation: animationFrames linear 0.8s
  -moz-animation-iteration-count: 1
  -moz-transform-origin: 50% 50%
  -o-animation: animationFrames linear 0.8s
  -o-animation-iteration-count: 1
  -o-transform-origin: 50% 50%
  -ms-animation: animationFrames linear 0.8s
  -ms-animation-iteration-count: 1
  -ms-transform-origin: 50% 50%

@keyframes animationFrames
  0%
    transform: translate(0px, 0px)

  15%
    transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  30%
    transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  45%
    transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  60%
    transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  75%
    transform: translate(1px, -5px)

  100%
    transform: translate(1px, 0px)

@-moz-keyframes animationFrames
  0%
    -moz-transform: translate(0px, 0px)

  15%
    -moz-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  30%
    -moz-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  45%

  60%
    -moz-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  75%
    -moz-transform: translate(1px, -5px)

  100%

@-webkit-keyframes animationFrames
  0%

  15%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  30%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  45%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  60%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  75%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, -5px)

  100%
    -webkit-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

@-o-keyframes animationFrames
  0%
    -o-transform: translate(0px, 0px)

  15%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  30%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  45%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, -10px)

  60%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  75%
    -o-transform: translate(1px, -5px)

  100%

@-ms-keyframes animationFrames

  45%

  60%
    -ms-transform: translate(1px, 0px)

  75%

  100%

sources.sass\\typograf.sass:
@import './grid'
%font
  font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif
%font-2
  font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive

%shadow
  box-shadow: 0px 10px 17px 0px rgba(34, 60, 80, 0.2)
  -moz-box-shadow: 0px 10px 17px 0px rgba(34, 60, 80, 0.2)
  -webkit-box-shadow: 0px 10px 17px 0px rgba(34, 60, 80, 0.2)


$color-1: #76aa6f
$red: #f96666
$gray: #f5f5f5
$gray-2: #93a6ab
$color-base: #000000
li, a
  @extend %font
a
  text-decoration: none
  color: $color-base
  font-weight: 600
  &:hover,&:active
    color: $color-1
.contact
  @extend %flex
  @extend %flex-row
  justify-content: center
  align-items: center
  // color: $color-1
  // font-size: 46px
  
//Format options
h1
  font:
    size: 3.157em
  line-height: $line
  margin-bottom: $base-line
h2
  font:
    size: 2.369em
  line-height: $line * 1.5
  margin-bottom: $base-line
h3
  font:
    size: 1.777em
  line-height: $line * 1.5
  margin-bottom: $base-line
h4
  font:
    size: 1.33em
  line-height: $line
  margin-bottom: $base-line
p
  line-height: $base-line * 1.618

img
  width: 100%
  margin: .5rem auto
  display: block

.section-h
  text-align: center
  margin: $base-line * 1
  &.cursiv
    @extend %font-2
    color: $color-1
    


=bg($img, $for: webp)
  background-image: url('../img/#{$img}.#{$for}')
=bga($img, $for: png)
  background-image: url('../img/#{$img}.#{$for}')
//Format options
sources.sass\\block\\_block-2.sass:
.b-2
  +bg(b-2,jpg)
  background-position: center
  background-size: cover
  .wrap
    padding: 5rem 0
    justify-content: center
  .img-content
    // background: #000
    display: flex
    justify-content: center
    align-items: center
    flex-direction: row
    .img-items
      margin: 0 1rem
    .block-namber
      font:
        size: $base-line * 4
        weight: 700
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.47843137254901963)
  .colum-flex
    @extend %flex
    @extend %flex-col
    justify-content: center
    background: rgba(241, 241, 241, 0.49)
    margin: $base-line 0
    border-radius: 10px
  h4
    text-align: center
    font-weight: 700
    color: #000000
sources.sass\\block\\_block-3.sass:
.b-3
  margin-top: $base-line * 5
  margin-bottom: $base-line * 5
  .card-items
    display: flex
    flex-direction: row
    justify-content: center
    padding: 2rem 0 !important
    &__button
      display: none
      position: absolute !important
      width: 100%
      background: #f5f5f5
      left: -1px
      border-top: 2px solid $color-1
      padding: 1rem 0 !important
      border-radius: 0px 0 10px 10px
      transition: all .2s ease
      div
        width: 83%
        margin: 0 auto
        background: $color-1
        border-radius: 5px
        color: #ffffff
        display: flex
        flex-direction: row
        justify-content: center
        align-items: center
      span
        @extend %font
        margin-left: 1rem
        font:
          size: $base-line * 1
        display: block
    &__box
      background: #f5f5f5
      width: 90%
      border-radius: 10px
      padding: 1rem !important
      padding-top: 2rem !important
      -webkit-box-shadow: -6px 2px 9px -1px rgba(34, 60, 80, 0.36)
      -moz-box-shadow: -6px 2px 9px -1px rgba(34, 60, 80, 0.36)
      box-shadow: -6px 2px 9px -1px rgba(34, 60, 80, 0.36)
      
      &:hover
        border: 0
        .card-items__button
          display: block

    &___badge
      position: absolute !important
      z-index: 5 !important
      right: 1rem
      top: .5rem
      background: $red
      color: #ffffff
      font:
        weight: 400
      float: right
      padding: .5rem .5rem !important
      border-radius: 5px
      &.new
        background: $gray-2
        color: $color-base
      &.none
        display: none
    &__img
      color: #ffffff
    &__name
      text-align: center
      font:
        weight: 700
        size: $base-line * 1.3
    &__price
      color: $color-1
      font:
        weight: 600
      text-align: center
    &__massa
      color: $red
      text-align: right
      margin-bottom: 2rem
sources.sass\\block\\_block-4.sass:
.b-4
  +bg(bg-pattern-1,jpg)
  
  background-position: bottom
  padding: $base-line * 4
  .owl-carousel.owl-drag,.owl-item
    padding: 1rem !important
  .owl-item
    display: flex
    flex-direction: row
    justify-content: center
    box-sizing: border-box !important
  .owl-nav
    display: flex
    flex-direction: row
    justify-content: center
  &> h3
    color: #000000
  .item
    width: 90%
    margin: 1rem 0
    background: #ffff
    border-radius: 10px
    padding: 2rem !important
    padding-top: 2rem !important
    -webkit-box-shadow: -6px 2px 9px -1px rgba(34, 60, 80, 0.36)
    -moz-box-shadow: -6px 2px 9px -1px rgba(34, 60, 80, 0.36)
    box-shadow: -6px 2px 9px -1px rgba(34, 60, 80, 0.36)
  &__text
    color: #777777
    font:
      size: $base-line * 1.3
    text-align: center
  &__info
    display: flex
    flex-direction: row
    margin: 1rem 0
    .img
      border-radius: 50px
      width: 70px
      height: 70px
      overflow: hidden
      margin-right: 2rem
      img
        background-position: top
        margin: 0 !important
    .author
      p
        color: $color-1
        font-size: $base-line * 1.2
